  "description": "<p><strong>We welcome:</strong><br />* Candidates with <u><strong>no experience</strong></u><br />* Fresh graduates<br />* Those who have completed ORD<br />* Individuals looking to change careers<br /><br /><strong>👀Who We Are Looking For</strong><br />* 18 years old and above<br />* Minimum 6-month commitment<br />* Singaporeans or PRs<br /><br /><strong>✨What We Value</strong><br />* Willingness to learn and improve<br />* Strong work ethic<br />* Motivation to earn while gaining valuable experience<br /><br /><strong>👉🏽Your Role</strong><br />* Engage and communicate with new people daily<br />* Represent our brand professionally<br />* Turn conversations into sales opportunities<br /><br /><strong>💫What We Offer</strong><br />* Full training and ongoing support<br />* Performance-based earnings with no earning cap<br />* Clear career progression opportunities* Friendly and supportive team environment<br />* Travel opportunities<br /><br /><br />If you’re looking for a role where you can learn, grow, and build a meaningful career, we’d be happy to connect with you.<br /><br /><br /><br /><br />Click <u><strong>APPLY NOW</strong></u> or contact <u><strong>8695 7302</strong></u> [A’syura] (WhatsApp)/ <strong>aruyys_a</strong> (Telegram)</p>",
